<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #00a63d;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #00a63d;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .header p {
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px 0;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            background-color: #00a63d;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #008f35;
        }
        .note {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="padding: 20px; background-color: #f4f4f4;">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>🎨 ArtVPP</h1>
                <p>College E-commerce for Student Artists</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <h2>Verify Your Email Address</h2>
                <p>Hi {{username}},</p>
                <p>
                    Thank you for registering with ArtVPP! To complete your signup and activate
                    your account, please verify your email address by clicking the button below.
                </p>

                <div class="button-container">
                    <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button" target="_blank">
                        Verify Email Address
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="note">
                    <strong>Note:</strong> This link will expire in 24 hours. If you didn't create
                    an account with ArtVPP, you can safely ignore this email.
                </div>

                <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">
                    If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
                    <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" style="color: #00a63d; word-break: break-all;">
                        {{verificationUrl}}
                    </a>
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="footer">
                <p>© {{year}} ArtVPP. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

